\frac{\sin 3A}{\sin 2A-\sin A}=\frac{\sin 3A}{2\sin A/2\cos 3A/2}\\=\frac{\sin 3A/2}{\sin A/2}=\frac{\sin A\cos A/2+\cos A\sin A/2}{\sin A/2}\\=\sin A\cot A/2+\cos A=2\cos^2A/2+\cos A=\cos A+1+\cos A=2\cos A+1
